Humans wont last long without water! Check out LARQ's Black Friday sale with up to 30% OFF: https://bylarq.com/Jerry Our backyard bunker has been empty for most of the summer. And during that vacancy... a bunch of spiders decided to make my backyard bunker their home.  Should we evict the invaders? Or should we burn it all with fire? 

Today we are going to connect my rainwater collection system to the bunker. That way - I can use my 3,000 gallons of stored rain water to water our garden, or survive an apocalypse. Whichever comes first.
